## üìä App Store Optimization Tips

### Title Optimization
- Include primary keyword "on-demand services"
- Keep under 30 characters for optimal display
- Make it memorable and brandable

### Description Structure
- Start with compelling hook
- Use bullet points for readability
- Include social proof and testimonials
- Clear call-to-action

### Screenshot Strategy
- First screenshot: Most compelling feature
- Show key functionality clearly
- Include text overlays explaining features
- Maintain consistent visual style

### Rating & Reviews
- Encourage satisfied users to rate
- Respond to all reviews promptly
- Address negative feedback constructively
- Use feedback to improve app

